{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/taxicab-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Brojevi za taksi","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Taxicab broj (definicija korišćena ovde) je pozitivan ceo broj koji se može predstaviti kao zbir dva kvadrata pozitivnih celih brojeva na više od jednog načina.</p>\n<p>Prvi broj taksija je <code>1729</code>, koji je:</p>\n<p>1<sup>3</sup> + 12<sup>3</sup> i</p>\n<p>9<sup>3</sup> + 10<sup>3</sup>.</p>\n<p>Brojevi za taksi kabl su takođe poznati kao:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>brojevi za taksi</li>\n  <li>brojevi za taksij-kab</li>\n  <li>brojevi za taksi kabl</li>\n  <li>brojevi Hardija-Ramanucana</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","id":"594ecc0d9a8cf816e3340187","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napišite funkciju koja vraća najniže dostupne brojeve taksija <code>n</code>. Za svaki broj taksija, prikažite taj broj zajedno sa njegovim podacima o dogovoru.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302337,"hooks":{"beforeAll":null,"beforeEach":"const res4 = [1729, 4104, 13832, 20683];\nconst res25 = [\n  1729, 4104, 13832, 20683, 32832, 39312, 40033, 46683, 64232, 65728, 110656,\n  110808, 134379, 149389, 165464, 171288, 195841, 216027, 216125, 262656, 314496, 320264, 327763,\n  373464, 402597\n];\n\nconst res39From20To29 = [314496, 320264, 327763, 373464, 402597, 439101, 443889, 513000, 513856];","afterEach":null,"afterAll":null},"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/taxicab-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function taxicabNumbers(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>taxicabNumbers</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof taxicabNumbers === 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>taxicabNumbers</code> Trebalo bi da vrati red podataka.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof taxicabNumbers(2) === 'object');"},{"text":"<p><code>taxicabNumbers</code> Trebalo bi da vrati red brojeva.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof taxicabNumbers(100)[0] === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>taxicabNumbers(4)</code> trebalo bi vratiti [1729, 4104, 13832, 20683].</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(taxicabNumbers(4), res4);"},{"text":"<p><code>taxicabNumbers(25)</code> treba da vrati [1729, 4104, 13832, 20683, 32832, 39312, 40033, 46683, 64232, 65728, 110656, 110808, 134379, 149389, 165464, 171288, 195841, 216027, 216125, 262656, 314496, 320264, 327763, 373464, 402597]</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(taxicabNumbers(25), res25);"},{"text":"<p><code>taxicabNumbers(39)</code> Brojevi koji potiču iz raspona 20–29 bi trebalo da budu [314496,320264,327763,373464,402597,439101,443889,513000,513856].</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(taxicabNumbers(39).slice(20, 29), res39From20To29);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"taxicab-numbers","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/tokenize-a-string-with-escaping","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/symmetric-difference","id":"594ecc0d9a8cf816e3340187","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/taxicab-numbers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}